Class PoisCategory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.marcoshsc.orsApiTools.pois.helperclasses.PoisCategory

  • public class PoisCategory
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a category, composed by an ID, the category name and the category group name. The ID is a osm ID, so you can search on the docs to see what each code mean.
